title: O-M-G BEST Crockpot Chicken EVER Recipe
directions: Throw everything in the crockpot on low and cook 6-8 hours.
After about 4 hours of cooking I usually stir everything together- but if you're not home it's no big deal.
Just stir about 20 minutes before serving to really mix together the cream cheese and dressing packets.
ingredients: 2 lbs boneless skinless Chicken Breasts (I like to dice them up so they're chicken tender sized)
